Subject: [PATCH] crypto/sha1: provide optimised assembly for riscv64
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Provide an optimised assembly implementation of sha1 for riscv64.

